#the juicy, usually blue, fruit of certain plants.
#a plant that bears blueberries.
#a dark [[blue]] [[color|colour]].
# (''geology'') a mineral formation first identified by the Mars Exploration Rover ''Opportunity'' in 2004, so-named because of its resemblance to blueberry muffins.  ''We see these strange round objects we're calling &ldquo;[[spherules]]&rdquo; embedded in the outcrop, like blueberries in a muffin.''

